      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power delivery with a spine-tingling 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock for superior lateral traction. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a recently reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain the platform's legendary handling precision. While the exterior displays minor patina expected of a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a documented valve clearance adjustment and cooling system refresh. This is a visceral, analog machine ready for the canyon roads.",
